# =========================
# Claude Code
# =========================
# Ignore everything under .claude/ by default,
# then re-allow shared, team-checked-in config.
CLAUDE.md
.claude/*
!.claude/settings.json
!.claude/commands/
!.claude/agents/
!.claude/hooks/
!.claude/skills/
.claude/settings.local.json
.claude/projects/
.claude/sessions/
.claude/memory/
.claude/todos/
.claude/shell-snapshots/
.claude/statsig/

# Local-only Claude memory (CLAUDE.md itself stays committed)
CLAUDE.local.md
**/CLAUDE.local.md
.claude.json
.claude.json.backup

